{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fdec304a94","title":"为古柏题写抚词","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"572f1f722c","index":0,"year":1937,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"fdec304a94"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji11","name":"毛泽东全集第11卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji11.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji11":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c3a865a145","type":"paragraph","text":"为古柏题写抚词","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"fdec304a94"},{"id":"b5c4db9ba6","type":"paragraph","text":"（1937年）吾友古柏，英俊奋发，为国捐钢，殊堪悲蚀。愿古氏同胞，继其遗志，共达自由解放之目的。[1]吉柏（1906-1935）男，汉族，江西省寻岛县人，中共党员1935年3月6日在广东龙川上坪街套坑被国民党军包围，在拖护同志们突围的战斗中英勇插性，年仅29岁。本文是耗传到延安后，毛泽东给古柏写的挖词。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"fdec304a94"}],"page":{"id":"c5ac0dd495","publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"fdec304a94","start":430,"end":430}}}},"__N_SSG":true}